{"tid":1721514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1115黎明行動 首爆港島線 中環金鐘集中火力","createTime":"2019-11-14T16:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T04:10:18.000Z","uid":111817,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"46807ec0bb83ac83fbf9940117f55f75e9110ed0","tid":1721514,"uid":111817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"連日黎已經好多手足同時要兼顧各大學+黎明行動<br />\n<br />\n不少手足係守城行動中已體力透支，人手有少無多，仲要黎明行動咁早起身，人手遠不如第一日黎明行動多<br />\n<br />\n所以一有人手，我地要主攻最大影響力既車站<br />\n<br />\n想返中環除非你係西隧，否則紅隧，港島線路面同黨鐵都被我地爆哂，依班人根本唔洗旨意返工<br />\n<br />\n無巴士無黨鐵無路面，全港最重要樞紐準備癱瘓啦！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>黎明行動，永不終止！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e6f4e017e510932ae22422999cb2ddbe49dbf0bd","tid":1721514,"uid":3865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"港島綫=春袋之一<br />\n推<br />\n<br />\n［旭日行動］唔好太依賴塞鐵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1721094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1721094</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d7b2dfdf4b5b03ab89674e9e37c9586af6b2729e","tid":1721514,"uid":111817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a71b88298a04be13861421d66f44042c0c2f40","tid":1721514,"uid":111817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde5590657d8a32e4ea6c4c6b22a5970b43c08b0","tid":1721514,"uid":111817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40afd3ad3db5582c000fbac5b6e024762f0f29e3","tid":1721514,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:22:21.000Z","msg":"嘩"},{"pid":"81386bb4adb86f77046f89f2dc203a8ee173f826","tid"